default5.5default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe majority of people 
defaultwho lose their job 
defaultwill only experience a short-term spell of unemployment. 
defaultOf the 325,000 unemployment claims that came to an end in June 2013, 53% of claimants were in receipt of JSA for 13 weeks or less
default. Shelter’s concern is that without an adequate safety net, people will be unable to bounce back and will be anxious about how
